(16671, 228, '_bptt_repeater_1_bptt__title', 'field_5a36ec565e795'),
(16672, 228, 'bptt_repeater_1_bptt__text', 'We’re Queensland’s most efficient internal crane truck door to door/site to site services. Depending on the order size HYBUILT can usually deliver your materials within 2-3 days after order confirmation. To efficiently carry out these duties HYBUILT operates an entire fleet of Crane Trucks in a variety of sizes to suit both Load size and/or potential access constraints.\r\n<div class="delivering-to">\r\n\r\nDelivering to:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Brisbane</li>\r\n 	<li>Gold Coast</li>\r\n 	<li>Ipswich</li>\r\n 	<li>Sunshine Coast</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>'),
