(27363, 277, 'instal_text', 'HYBUILT have partnered with only the most experienced Sandstone Installers across South East Queensland offering a complete Design &amp; Construct solution through competitive pricing and innovation.\r\n\r\nWe’ve quickly become Queensland\'s leading Sandstone Block Wall Installers &amp; Suppliers specialising in residential, industrial and civil projects.\r\n\r\nHYBUILT are arguably the most competitive installers in Queensland… How may you ask?… Through direct quarry supply arrangements coupled with effective and realistic pricing without ever compromising on quality.\r\n\r\nContact your HYBUILT representative now to book your next project.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/hybuilt/contact/">ENQUIRE</a>'),
